Name: Pets & Pickers
Title: Paws, Purrs, and Philanthropy
Desc: A Chihuahua gets rushed to RAPS after a car accident; a cat has an unknown object in her throat.
LongDescription: A lovable Chihuahua gets rushed to RAPS after a serious car accident; a one-year-old cat has an unknown object lodged in her throat; the surprises continue when a box of abandoned kittens is found outside RAPS.
